data.description: Your time is now! A popular open style, well maintained & move in ready Carrington Greene condo for sale! This unit boasts two bedrooms, two full baths an office/bonus room and an open concept. As you walk in you notice the space connects all rooms. The kitchen joins the dining room, the living then connect to the kitchen and bar area as well. It is simply perfect for entertaining. The primary suite has a bonus room for use as an office, work out room or whatever your heart desires. The garden patio can be accessed from the living room or from the office/bonus room as well. Lovely afternoon light fills the home nicely. The rear entry two-car garage has nice attic space for storage as well.  This patio home is located at the end of the street which allows for lots of privacy and security.
